text: Re-boot is the first studio album by South Korean band, Golden Child. The album was released on 18 November 2019 by recording label, Woollim Entertainment. Consists of 12 songs, the track "WANNABE" was chosen as the title track for the album. ==Track listings== ==Release history== Region Date Format Label/Distributor Reference 18 November 2019 Digital download Online streaming Worldwide == References == ==Other websites== * * Music sites: Category:2019 albums
